channel.title: Messed up enviromenal veriables
channel.description: ok i tryed to make a server so i gave up deleted all the java crap in the enviromental veriables user file and stuff i got java version 13 how do i fix it so i can play rs private servers again??

item.title: Messed up enviromenal veriables
item.dc:creator: @Jessekinss Jessekinss
item.description:
@Jessekinss wrote:

Re-downloading java would fix that problem, you don’t need to set up environmental variables to run a client.
If you’re trying to set up another server then copy and paste the path of your java to “PATH” and “JAVA_HOME” in your variables.
